<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Confirmaci√≥n de Orden - ZayrelStudio</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .header p {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 22px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .message {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .order-number {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }

        .order-number p {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .order-number .number {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #667eea;
            font-family: monospace;
        }

        .items-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }

        .items-table th {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #666;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .items-table td {
            padding: 15px 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .item-name {
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .item-details {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .totals {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }

        .totals-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 8px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .totals-row.total {
            border-top: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding-top: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #333;
        }

        .payment-method {
            background: #e8f4fd;
            border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }

        .payment-method p {
            color: #1565c0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .shipping-address {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .shipping-address h3 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .shipping-address p {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #fff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 16px 40px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .next-steps {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }

        .next-steps p {
            color: #856404;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #2d3748;
            color: #a0aec0;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #667eea;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üõçÔ∏è ¬°Orden Confirmada!</h1>
            <p>Gracias por tu compra en ZayrelStudio</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2 class="greeting">Hola {{customerName}},</h2>

            <p class="message">
                Hemos recibido tu orden correctamente. A continuaci√≥n encontrar√°s los detalles de tu pedido.
            </p>

            <div class="order-number">
                <p>N√∫mero de Orden</p>
                <span class="number">#{{orderNumber}}</span>
            </div>

            <table class="items-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Producto</th>
                        <th style="text-align: center;">Cant.</th>
                        <th style="text-align: right;">Precio</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {{#each items}}
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <div class="item-name">{{this.name}}</div>
                            {{#if this.size}}
                            <div class="item-details">{{this.color}} / {{this.size}}</div>
                            {{/if}}
                        </td>
                        <td style="text-align: center;">{{this.quantity}}</td>
                        <td style="text-align: right;">{{currency this.total}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    {{/each}}
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <div class="totals">
                <div class="totals-row">
                    <span>Subtotal</span>
                    <span>{{currency subtotal}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="totals-row">
                    <span>Env√≠o</span>
                    <span>{{#if freeShipping}}GRATIS{{else}}{{currency shippingCost}}{{/if}}</span>
                </div>
                {{#if discount}}
                <div class="totals-row" style="color: #22c55e;">
                    <span>Descuento</span>
                    <span>-{{currency discount}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                <div class="totals-row total">
                    <span>Total</span>
                    <span>{{currency total}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="payment-method">
                <p>üí≥ <strong>M√©todo de pago:</strong> {{paymentMethodDisplay}}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="shipping-address">
                <h3>üìç Direcci√≥n de Env√≠o</h3>
                <p>
                    {{shippingAddress.street}}<br>
                    {{shippingAddress.city}}, {{shippingAddress.state}}<br>
                    {{shippingAddress.country}}<br>
                    Tel: {{shippingAddress.phone}}
                </p>
            </div>

            {{#if isManualPayment}}
            <div class="next-steps">
                <p>‚è≥ <strong>Pr√≥ximo paso:</strong> Realiza tu transferencia o SINPE y sube el comprobante en "Mis √ìrdenes" para que podamos verificar tu pago.</p>
            </div>
            {{else}}
            <div class="next-steps">
                <p>‚è≥ <strong>Estado:</strong> Estamos procesando tu pago. Te notificaremos cuando sea confirmado.</p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
                <a href="{{orderUrl}}" class="cta-button">Ver mi Orden</a>
            </div>

            <p style="color: #333; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 30px;">
                ¬°Gracias por confiar en nosotros!<br>
                <strong>El equipo de {{brandName}}</strong>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>¬© {{year}} {{brandName}}. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px;">
                <a href="{{instagramUrl}}">Instagram</a> ‚Ä¢
                <a href="{{siteUrl}}">Web</a>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11px;">
                Este correo fue enviado a {{email}} porque realizaste una compra.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
